	"content": "<h1 class=\"page-title\">Office Hours</h1>\n  \n  <div id=\"todo-date-mount-point\"></div>\n  \n    <p>Please visit office hours throughout the semester to make sure you are not falling behind. You have resources...use them!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>TA Office Hours</strong></span></p>\n<p>All TA office hours have a Zoom option and use the same Zoom link: <a class=\"inline_disabled external\" href=\"https://cuboulder.zoom.us/j/97669455338\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><span>ZOOM LINK</span><span class=\"external_link_icon\" style=\"margin-inline-start: 5px; display: inline-block; text-indent: initial; \" role=\"presentation\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1920 1920\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"width:1em; height:1em; vertical-align:middle; fill:currentColor\">\n    <path d=\"M1226.667 267c88.213 0 160 71.787 160 160v426.667H1280v-160H106.667v800C106.667 1523 130.56 1547 160 1547h1066.667c29.44 0 53.333-24 53.333-53.333v-213.334h106.667v213.334c0 88.213-71.787 160-160 160H160c-88.213 0-160-71.787-160-160V427c0-88.213 71.787-160 160-160Zm357.706 442.293 320 320c20.8 20.8 20.8 54.614 0 75.414l-320 320-75.413-75.414 228.907-228.906H906.613V1013.72h831.254L1508.96 784.707l75.413-75.414Zm-357.706-335.626H160c-29.44 0-53.333 24-53.333 53.333v160H1280V427c0-29.333-23.893-53.333-53.333-53.333Z\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"></path>\n</svg>\n<span class=\"screenreader-only\">Links to an external site.</span></span></a></p>\n<p>Some office hours are also in person, which will show a room# next to the time.</p>\n<p><span class=\"instructure_file_holder link_holder instructure_file_link_holder\"><a class=\"inline_disabled preview_in_overlay\" title=\"TA Calendar - December.pdf\" href=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/courses/121531/files/81818369?wrap=1\" target=\"_blank\" data-canvas-previewable=\"false\" data-api-endpoint=\"https://canvas.colorado.edu/api/v1/courses/121531/files/81818369\" data-api-retu